00:17.309 --> 00:19.394
<i>For years, losing my virginity</i>

00:19.478 --> 00:21.396
<i>felt just as impossible
as losing the weight.</i>

00:21.480 --> 00:23.440
<i>So I hadn't given it much thought.</i>

00:23.982 --> 00:24.983
<i>But now...</i>

00:25.692 --> 00:28.987
<i>I wanted to take out my new body
and see what it could do.</i>

00:31.990 --> 00:35.035
<i>I still wasn't totally comfortable
in my new skin.</i>

00:35.118 --> 00:38.455
<i>But feeling Brick's skin against mine
was driving me crazy.</i>

00:38.539 --> 00:42.084
<i>I was making out with the guy
I'd been crushing on since junior high.</i>

00:42.167 --> 00:44.795
<i>It was my schoolgirl fantasy come true.</i>

00:46.296 --> 00:48.048
<i>I didn't care if it was love.</i>

00:48.507 --> 00:51.385
<i>For the first time in my life,
I was hungry</i>

00:51.468 --> 00:52.970
<i>for something other than food.</i>

00:53.345 --> 00:55.347
<i>And I wanted more.</i>

00:55.430 --> 00:58.141
Wow, wow. Hey, slow down.

00:58.850 --> 01:00.602
Why? Am I doing something wrong?

01:00.686 --> 01:02.187
No. I just...

01:02.604 --> 01:06.692
I really like you and Magnolia
always said I was going too fast, so.

01:06.775 --> 01:08.193
I'm not Magnolia.

01:09.486 --> 01:11.196
Unless you're not sure?

01:11.863 --> 01:13.323
Are you not attracted to me?

01:13.407 --> 01:16.618
No, no, no. No. I am.

01:16.702 --> 01:18.370
I definitely am.

01:18.745 --> 01:19.621
I...

01:20.497 --> 01:21.456
I just...

01:21.748 --> 01:23.500
I still think it should be special.

01:24.042 --> 01:25.836
Let me do something nice for you.

01:25.919 --> 01:27.462
I know what you can do for me.

01:30.048 --> 01:31.758
Oh my God.

01:33.135 --> 01:35.512
Magnolia's freaking
that you're not returning her texts.

01:35.846 --> 01:38.557
She's asking me if I think
you're hooking up with someone else.

01:38.640 --> 01:39.725
You guys are friends?

01:39.808 --> 01:42.519
We won't be for long
if she finds out about us.

01:43.020 --> 01:46.940
God, it's so unfair.
Magnolia gets everything she wants.

01:47.024 --> 01:49.484
Pageant crowns and friends and you.

01:49.568 --> 01:52.821
Now that's finally my turn, she gets
to make me feel guilty about it.

01:52.904 --> 01:53.739
Hey.

01:54.114 --> 01:55.449
I won't tell her if you don't.

01:57.826 --> 01:59.161
Could you also not tell your dad?

02:00.120 --> 02:03.165
He'll just get worried that you're gonna
distract me from Miss Magic Jesus.

02:03.248 --> 02:06.209
Trust me, the last thing I want
is for him to get involved.

02:11.131 --> 02:12.466
Why won't Magnolia...

02:12.549 --> 02:13.925
Oh, it's your dad.

02:14.843 --> 02:15.677
Crap!

02:16.845 --> 02:18.930
I gotta go get my baptism certificate.

02:21.224 --> 02:22.809
- Could you give me a ride?
- Mm-hm.

02:28.732 --> 02:30.275
You were never baptized?

02:30.359 --> 02:33.111
Patty, I asked you about this weeks ago!

02:35.697 --> 02:37.866
I assumed that I was.

02:37.949 --> 02:40.535
I know we don't go to church,
but we're in the Bible Belt.

02:40.619 --> 02:42.788
Everyone I know has been baptized,
even Jews.

02:42.871 --> 02:44.039
Why would I be the exception?

02:44.581 --> 02:47.084
I kept meaning to do it.

02:47.668 --> 02:50.504
I was kinda busy after you were born,
making up six...

02:50.587 --> 02:52.005
nine months of not drinking.

02:53.298 --> 02:57.010
Besides, you don't really
believe in all that stuff, do you?

02:57.552 --> 02:59.596
What, God? A higher power?

02:59.680 --> 03:01.765
The thing that you said got you sober

03:01.848 --> 03:03.767
and kept you from ending up dead
in a ditch?

03:03.850 --> 03:06.478
You're right.
Why would I believe in any of that?

03:06.561 --> 03:10.232
I figured maybe you would protect
my immortal soul from eternal damnation.

03:10.315 --> 03:11.817
You know, just in case hell is real.

03:11.900 --> 03:14.277
Oh, it is real. All right?

03:14.361 --> 03:18.198
Without that baptism certificate,
you are in pageant purgatory.

03:18.281 --> 03:20.742
No Miss Magic Jesus,
no Miss American Lady.

03:20.826 --> 03:23.870
I have to talk to Pastor Mike
before orientation.

03:23.954 --> 03:24.788
Pastor who?

03:24.871 --> 03:26.873
He just took over
the Fourth Baptist Church.

03:26.957 --> 03:29.376
He is in charge of the pageant.

03:29.459 --> 03:33.255
Maybe he'll make an exception,
show us some of the Lord's mercy.

03:33.338 --> 03:36.466
No way, Jose. Look.

03:37.634 --> 03:41.430
I may be new to the whole pageant thing,
but it's just common sense.

03:41.513 --> 03:45.517
Patty can't be in a pageant called
Miss Magic Jesus if she isn't baptized.

03:45.851 --> 03:47.978
It just wouldn't be kosher.

03:48.061 --> 03:51.773
Well, could you do a quickie baptism,
you know, like a dunk 'n' go?

03:52.274 --> 03:56.194
I don't do dunk 'n' goes.
The big boss wouldn't approve.

03:56.278 --> 03:59.239
- The big boss?
- God, Bob.

03:59.322 --> 04:01.241
And you don't wanna piss him off.

04:02.117 --> 04:04.703
I'd have to baptize Patty properly.

04:04.786 --> 04:07.914
She would need spiritual counseling first
and then godparents.

04:07.998 --> 04:09.833
Well, is one enough?

04:09.916 --> 04:11.084
I suppose so.

04:11.168 --> 04:14.421
Great. Then I will be her godfather.

04:15.297 --> 04:17.673
Are you sure you are up to the task?

04:18.425 --> 04:22.554
Isn't it like you just say,
I'm her godfather and then it's done?

04:22.637 --> 04:25.432
- Like bibbidy bobbidi...
- That's a fairy godmother, Bob.

04:25.515 --> 04:26.683
Right. Got it.

04:26.767 --> 04:30.103
You would be pledging to be
Patty's spiritual mentor and role model

04:30.187 --> 04:31.480
for her entire life.

04:32.355 --> 04:35.567
Do you feel that you embody
the Fruits of the Spirit?

04:36.526 --> 04:37.778
I mean, yeah.

04:37.861 --> 04:40.989
I feel like my insides
are appropriately fruity.

04:43.533 --> 04:45.327
You wanna be my godfather?

04:45.410 --> 04:47.829
I have to be,
if we're gonna get you baptized.

04:47.913 --> 04:50.040
Otherwise, Pastor Mike
won't let you compete.

04:50.123 --> 04:52.375
I'm already your coach.

04:52.459 --> 04:53.710
It's not that big a leap,

04:53.794 --> 04:56.713
except being responsible for you
for the rest of your life.

04:57.214 --> 04:58.799
'Til death do us part?

04:59.174 --> 05:01.843
Hmm, more like a father figure.

05:01.927 --> 05:04.763
Meet me in Pastor Mike's office
as soon as orientation is over.

05:04.846 --> 05:06.598
We'll start spiritual counseling.

05:06.681 --> 05:08.892
<i>I've never looked
at Bob as a father.</i>

05:08.975 --> 05:12.813
<i>He was always more of a DILF,
but I was dating Bob's son.</i>

05:12.896 --> 05:15.899
<i>So, why not put Bob
in charge of my Holy Spirit?</i>

05:15.982 --> 05:18.360
- Move out of the way, Fatty.
- Suck it, Dixie.

05:18.860 --> 05:20.529
Not you. Her.

05:20.821 --> 05:23.281
Wasn't the plus-size pageant last week?

05:23.365 --> 05:25.492
Wasn't the pocket-sized pageant
last month?

05:25.575 --> 05:29.079
Or did you make a wrong turn
on the way to <i>Smurfs, the Musical?</i>

05:29.162 --> 05:31.373
It's cool. I got this.

05:31.790 --> 05:32.999
I like the way I look.

05:33.250 --> 05:34.501
That's why I do pageants.

05:34.584 --> 05:37.838
To show people that beauty
comes in all shapes and sizes.

05:38.338 --> 05:40.507
Even short little mofos like you.

05:40.590 --> 05:42.384
I think you might be my new best friend.

05:42.467 --> 05:44.594
I thought I was your new best friend.

05:45.470 --> 05:46.721
Did you get my text?

05:47.639 --> 05:49.474
Yeah, sorry. I was tied up.

05:51.268 --> 05:54.896
So, what do you think?
Is Brick seeing someone else?

05:55.814 --> 05:58.817
No way.
I'm sure you're just being paranoid.

05:58.900 --> 06:01.403
I saw you kiss him
at the dog wash, you slut!

06:04.364 --> 06:06.241
I gave you the chance to come clean

06:06.324 --> 06:09.327
and you just kept digging yourself
deeper and deeper into a hole.

06:09.911 --> 06:12.622
Screw you and your hole.
Nobody messes with my sister.

06:13.623 --> 06:15.333
We are not sisters.

06:15.417 --> 06:18.336
Yes, we are. We share a bedroom.
And a toothbrush.

06:18.420 --> 06:20.755
I knew you were using my toothbrush.
Don't do that.

06:21.715 --> 06:24.050
And you, you broke the girl code.

06:24.134 --> 06:26.553
You can't steal your friend's boyfriend.

06:26.636 --> 06:28.763
I didn't steal him.
You guys were broken up.

06:28.847 --> 06:31.892
I told you I wanted him back
and you went after him anyway.

06:31.975 --> 06:33.768
Could you be anymore selfish?

06:33.852 --> 06:36.271
You're selfish. Brick is happy.

06:36.354 --> 06:39.482
You dumped him
and now he likes me, so get over it.

06:41.067 --> 06:43.737
Oh, no she didn't.

06:44.821 --> 06:47.616
You think you're hot shit now
because you're skinny?

06:48.867 --> 06:50.619
You're a basic bitch.

06:50.702 --> 06:54.289
And I'm gonna beat your ass
in this pageant and every other pageant

06:54.372 --> 06:55.957
until the end of time.

06:56.041 --> 06:59.336
Hello, ladies.
Welcome to Miss Magic Jesus.

06:59.419 --> 07:00.712
Everybody take a seat.

07:00.795 --> 07:03.006
And if the choir
would start us off, please.

07:08.345 --> 07:10.722
What did she mean,
"now that you're skinny"?

07:11.765 --> 07:15.268
I lost 70 pounds.
So now it's my turn to get the guy.

07:17.604 --> 07:20.482
Being skinny don't mean shit
if you're ugly on the inside.

07:26.154 --> 07:29.658
Patty, the act of baptism means
dying to your old self

07:29.741 --> 07:32.953
and committing yourself
to a Christly existence.

07:33.828 --> 07:36.790
Jesus was so fully committed
to serving others,

07:36.873 --> 07:39.167
he was willing to die for their sins.

07:39.793 --> 07:41.836
A woman worthy of winning Miss Magic Jesus

07:41.920 --> 07:46.091
needs to focus on serving others,
instead of self-gratification.

07:46.174 --> 07:48.134
- What? No.
- Patty.

07:48.218 --> 07:50.261
I'm sorry.
What's wrong with self-gratification?

07:51.137 --> 07:54.224
I deserve to be happy.
I've spent years being miserable.

07:54.307 --> 07:57.394
The source of all misery is selfishness.

07:58.103 --> 07:59.312
That's the original sin.

08:00.480 --> 08:02.607
And I bet you could think of examples
from your own life

08:02.691 --> 08:06.820
when acting on selfish impulses
has caused pain to you or other people.

08:09.155 --> 08:10.073
Well I...

08:11.533 --> 08:14.494
I did just kiss my friend's boyfriend.
Or ex-boyfriend.

08:15.120 --> 08:16.371
And now she's really mad at me.

08:16.454 --> 08:19.749
- Wait, what?
- And I may have broken up Bob's marriage.

08:20.375 --> 08:22.961
Wow. You mean,
you two are "involved"?

08:23.044 --> 08:24.504
Absolutely not.

08:25.422 --> 08:32.095
Patty, let it slip to my wife
that I had an affair twenty years ago.

08:32.178 --> 08:33.388
Which I regret.

08:34.304 --> 08:37.267
Coralee is taking a break to think.

08:38.852 --> 08:41.020
And how's the rest of your family
taking the separation?

08:42.022 --> 08:44.149
I... Ugh, I don't know.

08:44.232 --> 08:48.903
My daughter's in Iraq and my son Brick
and I don't talk that much, so.

08:48.987 --> 08:51.656
Bob, you can't be
a good godfather to Patty

08:51.740 --> 08:54.200
if you can't be a good father to your son.

08:54.909 --> 08:59.080
And being a parent is the perfect way
to practice being of service.

08:59.956 --> 09:01.916
Trust me, I know.

09:02.459 --> 09:04.044
You have children?

09:04.627 --> 09:05.503
A son.

09:06.004 --> 09:07.172
Christian.

09:10.884 --> 09:15.680
You guys, this baptism
is a perfect opportunity

09:15.764 --> 09:17.474
for you both to change your lives.

09:17.557 --> 09:20.018
But you cannot reap the benefits
of being of service

09:20.101 --> 09:22.270
if you don't do the footwork first.

09:23.688 --> 09:24.773
So, where do we start?

09:25.940 --> 09:29.444
You should each pick
a simple act of selflessness.

09:29.694 --> 09:32.322
Bob, you should reach out to your son.

09:32.405 --> 09:34.365
Do something nice for him.

09:34.449 --> 09:37.619
And Patty, you might wanna
reach out to your friend.

09:37.702 --> 09:41.247
The one whose boyfriend you stole.
Might be a good way to make amends.

09:42.582 --> 09:45.752
Now if you both pursue this in earnest,

09:46.252 --> 09:49.714
I will baptize Patty
in time for Miss Magic Jesus.

09:49.881 --> 09:53.676
But, mark my words,
if you don't take it seriously,

09:53.760 --> 09:54.886
I will know.

09:54.969 --> 09:57.847
<i>I didn't believe this God stuff,
but he would never know.</i>

09:57.931 --> 10:00.683
<i>I did love my son
and I needed to get Patty baptized, so...</i>

10:00.767 --> 10:02.977
Bob, I'm serious.

10:03.061 --> 10:05.772
I have been blessed
with the gift of discernment.

10:06.523 --> 10:10.318
I can put my hands on someone's body
and see into their soul.

10:11.361 --> 10:12.403
I'll prove it.

10:22.455 --> 10:23.748
You were desperate.

10:25.083 --> 10:28.419
Ready to throw in the towel, end it all.

10:28.795 --> 10:29.921
<i>End it all?</i>

10:30.004 --> 10:32.382
<i>He couldn't possibly know
about the gun in my glove box.</i>

10:32.465 --> 10:33.716
But she saved you.

10:33.800 --> 10:34.884
Okay, that's enough.

10:35.969 --> 10:38.138
Um, so we will see you tomorrow.

10:41.349 --> 10:42.600
Be of service.

10:44.435 --> 10:48.648
<i>Maybe Pastor Mike was right.
With God, all things were possible.</i>

10:49.190 --> 10:51.776
<i>I could save my soul and win the crown.</i>

10:52.152 --> 10:55.238
<i>But first things first,
I needed to get baptized.</i>

10:55.321 --> 10:58.283
<i>Which meant I needed to do
something nice for Magnolia.</i>

10:58.867 --> 11:00.952
I'm gonna set Magnolia up with Christian.

11:02.120 --> 11:04.747
It's like a good deed
to make up for dating her ex.

11:04.831 --> 11:06.875
Couldn't you just stop dating Brick?

11:06.958 --> 11:08.042
I don't want to.

11:08.126 --> 11:12.088
Besides, Brick likes me now and Christian
and Magnolia are perfect for each other.

11:12.172 --> 11:15.466
He's hot, available, and they already know
each other 'cause he's her drug dealer.

11:15.550 --> 11:17.385
Sounds divinely inspired.

11:17.468 --> 11:19.596
Just don't become too
pure to watch Drew eat human flesh

11:19.679 --> 11:22.098
because we're binging season one
of <i>Santa Clarita Diet.</i>

11:22.182 --> 11:23.892
Oh, I can't.

11:23.975 --> 11:28.271
I've just got a lot to do this weekend
with the pageant and getting baptized

11:28.354 --> 11:29.689
and Brick.

11:29.772 --> 11:31.941
We'll watch it next weekend, I promise.

11:33.985 --> 11:35.612
I'll watch <i>Santa Clarita Diet</i> with you.

11:37.030 --> 11:38.323
It's not the same.

11:38.406 --> 11:41.034
So, do you wanna do something else?

11:41.451 --> 11:43.953
There's an open mic night
at a coffee house I like.

11:44.746 --> 11:47.123
You like to hang out in coffee houses?

11:47.749 --> 11:49.667
There's more to Choi than meets the eye.

11:55.298 --> 11:56.216
Hey.

11:56.799 --> 11:58.593
I think you should ask out
Magnolia Bernard.

11:58.676 --> 11:59.886
I think I should ask you out.

12:01.471 --> 12:03.556
Um, no. You screwed me over.

12:03.640 --> 12:04.766
Remember?

12:04.849 --> 12:06.726
Besides, you're a drug dealer.

12:06.809 --> 12:08.478
So judgmental.

12:09.229 --> 12:11.648
And anyway, I'm dating Brick Armstrong.

12:11.731 --> 12:14.442
Good for you. There's just one problem.

12:15.443 --> 12:17.862
You're not into Brick. You're into me.

12:18.780 --> 12:19.989
- That's not true.
- No?

12:20.365 --> 12:21.532
Hmm-mm.

12:21.616 --> 12:23.284
Why do you want me to ask out Magnolia?

12:23.368 --> 12:26.996
Because I'm trying to do something nice
for her by setting her up with a hot guy.

12:27.080 --> 12:28.581
Oh, see?

12:30.625 --> 12:31.793
You think I'm hot.

12:33.002 --> 12:34.254
That's not the point.

12:34.337 --> 12:39.550
So, you're not... feeling anything?

12:39.634 --> 12:41.886
Nope.

12:44.389 --> 12:45.265
Nothing at all?

12:45.348 --> 12:47.433
Hmm-mm.

12:49.852 --> 12:52.438
Then I'll never...

12:54.607 --> 12:55.733
ever...

12:57.986 --> 12:58.987
kiss you.

13:00.446 --> 13:01.781
Thanks for the tip about Magnolia.

13:08.579 --> 13:10.915
Hey. I have a proposition for you.

13:11.624 --> 13:12.875
I'm listening.

13:12.959 --> 13:15.920
I hear you're pissed
Brick is seeing Patty Bladell.

13:16.004 --> 13:17.255
You want him back?

13:17.338 --> 13:19.299
Why is this any of your business?

13:20.049 --> 13:23.636
What better way to make Brick jealous
than go out with the guy he hates most?

13:25.013 --> 13:26.472
What's in it for you?

13:26.848 --> 13:30.893
I'm into Patty and she's into me.
She's just in denial right now.

13:30.977 --> 13:34.856
So, you think if we go out...
it'll make them both crazy?

13:34.939 --> 13:37.775
Yeah. Like in one of those
stupid movies from the 80's.

13:38.568 --> 13:42.113
We could go to Brick's wrestling match,
make a spectacle of ourselves.

13:42.196 --> 13:46.451
I love spectacles.
Like the circus. I'll bring snacks.

13:46.534 --> 13:47.744
You are not coming.

13:47.827 --> 13:50.830
But I'm lonely! And I miss my momma.

13:51.331 --> 13:52.832
I have nobody to plot with.

13:52.915 --> 13:55.293
And now you're plotting revenge
and I want in.

13:55.376 --> 13:57.170
It's not a plot.

13:58.504 --> 13:59.380
It's a date.

14:04.677 --> 14:05.511
Hey.

14:07.638 --> 14:11.476
My dad has a pastry cooking class tonight,
so we'll have the house all to ourselves.

14:14.312 --> 14:15.480
It'd be really special.

14:20.818 --> 14:22.320
<i>Pastor Mike was right.</i>

14:22.403 --> 14:25.198
<i>I'd done something selfless,
and I was being rewarded.</i>

14:25.281 --> 14:28.159
<i>Maybe I could be of service to Brick too.</i>

14:32.789 --> 14:36.334
Hey, buddy. I was thinking about our talk.

14:36.417 --> 14:38.628
About how we never spend time together,

14:38.711 --> 14:42.090
and I was thinking maybe I could take you
shopping for some new clothes or...

14:42.173 --> 14:43.841
No, thanks. I have a date.

14:46.302 --> 14:50.431
Changing your own sheets? Roses, candles.

14:51.015 --> 14:53.017
You are having a sex date.

14:53.101 --> 14:55.186
Don't you have a pastry class to get to?

14:55.436 --> 14:57.522
- Are you back together with Magnolia?
- No.

14:58.815 --> 14:59.816
Well, who is it?

15:00.400 --> 15:01.609
None of your business.

15:03.569 --> 15:05.780
Is it another mom from school?

15:09.742 --> 15:10.618
Not funny, Dad.

15:10.701 --> 15:12.203
I agree.

15:12.286 --> 15:14.872
The fact that you had sex
with the one person

15:14.956 --> 15:16.666
I hate the most in the world

15:16.749 --> 15:18.167
is not funny. It's not funny at all.

15:18.251 --> 15:19.627
I'm not talking to you about this.

15:19.710 --> 15:21.379
Oh, I think we should.

15:23.131 --> 15:24.966
Did you do it to get back at me?

15:25.049 --> 15:27.885
You think I slept with Regina
because of you?

15:27.969 --> 15:31.514
I know that you were angry
that I am not more involved in your life.

15:31.597 --> 15:34.642
Maybe you did it
to try and get my attention.

15:34.725 --> 15:36.978
- I did it to get laid.
- Okay.

15:37.061 --> 15:38.729
Trust me, when I was with Regina,

15:38.813 --> 15:41.107
you were the last person
I was thinking about.

15:41.190 --> 15:42.859
But once again, thank you.

15:42.942 --> 15:44.902
Thank you for making everything
about yourself.

15:44.986 --> 15:46.571
Mom's right, you are a narcissist.

15:46.654 --> 15:49.532
Yeah. The last time I talked to her,
she called you that.

